\s Kule muji wa Daudi
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Kule muji wa Daudi pa\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd li kulisha nyama, Mama alimulalisha Mwana wake na mapendo\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Mama yule ni Maria, Mwana wake Yesu Kristo.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Yesu aliacha\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd , akakuja duniani, Nyumba yake, zizi bule\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  na kitanda chake, nyasi\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Alikuwa masikini na munyenyekevu sana.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Siku za watoto wake, vile siku za ujana, Mwana wa kusikiliza, alitii mama yake\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Na watoto waamini wanapashwa kuwa hivi.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Alikwenda pa\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd li pote, akifanya kazi njema, Naye akawaponyesha watu wengi wa ugongwa\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Akakufa kwa \bd*\bd Kalvari\bd*\bd  kwa ajili yetu yote.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Tutamwona waziwazi, kwani ametukomboa\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Mwana yule ni Mwokozi, vile Bwana wa wabwana\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Naye anatuongoza hata atakaporudi.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Hututamukuta tena pa\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd li pa kulisha nyuma\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Tutamwona kule\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd , Bwana mwenye utukufu\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Kama nyota watu wake watamuzunguka wote.\bd*
